OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day.
OL,6,FA fair amount of cloud around this
OL,7,Fmorning but this breaking to allow
OL,8,Fsome bright or sunny spells this
OL,9,Fafternoon. Rather cool, especially
OL,10,Falong the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will be dry with clear periods
OL,15,Fbut the east may become cloudy.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FDry with plenty of sunshine
OL,18,Fbut eastern Aberdeenshire may be
OL,19,Frather cool and cloudy. Warm inland,
OL,20,Flocally very warm across Moray.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
