OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry on
OL,6,FFriday with bright spells, western
OL,7,FAberdeenshire will be rather cloudy.
OL,8,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east on
OL,9,FSaturday. A few showers possible on
OL,10,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
